Demonstration material disclaimer
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Several modules in this repository ship JURISDICTION_RULE_PRESETS,
sample policy fixtures, and example actions explicitly marked as
DEMONSTRATION ONLY (e.g. the Title vertical's MT / OR / CA / TX / FL
rule packs, the demonstration outbound submission transport, and the
sample APL policies under examples/). These materials illustrate the
SHAPE of a deployable rule set or transport; they are not legal advice
and are not validated for production use against any regulator, DMV,
ELT hub, or other government endpoint. Real deployments require
counsel review and per-jurisdiction certification onboarding before
any rule pack or transport may be promoted past
`rule_validation_state: "demonstration"` or
`production_validated: false`.
